Risk Pattern
├── Decision Latency      @tag: stakeholder
├── Dependency Slip       @tag: technical
└── Resourcing Gap        @tag: capacity

## Inheritance Rules

If a workstream is tagged Dependency Slip and references unknown integration effort,
it should also inherit Resourcing Gap until ownership is explicit.
